replies.bodyText:
I am configuring the sensor with the commands BEFORE I register the listener.
I found it a lot easier to do the protocol stuff in a synchronous manner so I have commands and their replies in one place to check if they belong together and there are no errors.
So this is all done before the calls:
localSerialPort.notifyOnDataAvailable(true);
localSerialPort.addEventListener(this);

